---
// Timeline.astro
---

<div class="timeline-container">
  <h3 class="timeline-title"><span class="marker-highlight">Consensus</span>: Engagement Strategy</h3>

  <div class="tl-wrap">

    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-node accent"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-1 skew-left interactive-hover">
        <div class="tl-card-inner">
          <div class="tl-text">
            <div class="phase accent">Phase 1</div>
            <span class="time-label accent">1–4 months</span>
            <h4>Listening Sessions</h4>
            <p>Gathering feedback from Gowanus residents and local studio artists on ideal studio viewing path.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-image">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/phase1.jpg`} alt="Community listening session" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-gap gap-1"></div>

    <div class="tl-item right">
      <div class="tl-node dark"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-2 skew-right interactive-hover">
        <div class="tl-card-inner reverse">
          <div class="tl-image">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/phase2.jpg`} alt="Design workshop" />
          </div>
          <div class="tl-text">
            <div class="phase dark">Phase 2</div>
            <span class="time-label dark">4–9 months</span>
            <h4>Design and Iteration</h4>
            <p>Collaborative workshops to outline the 'Art Spine' route, balancing safety and aesthetics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-gap gap-2"></div>

    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-node accent"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-1 skew-left interactive-hover">
        <div class="tl-card-inner">
          <div class="tl-text">
            <div class="phase accent">Phase 3</div>
            <span class="time-label accent">9–12 months</span>
            <h4>Pilot Program</h4>
            <p>Temporary street closures and weekend art walks to test the impact of the spine.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-image">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/phase3.jpg`} alt="Pilot street closure" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-gap gap-3"></div>

    <div class="tl-item right">
      <div class="tl-node dark"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-2 skew-right interactive-hover">
        <div class="tl-card-inner reverse">
          <div class="tl-image">
            <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/images/phase4.jpg`} alt="Completed streetscape" />
          </div>
          <div class="tl-text">
            <div class="phase dark">Phase 4</div>
            <span class="time-label dark">Year 2 and beyond</span>
            <h4>Implementation</h4>
            <p>Permanent zoning adjustments and streetscaping for the full Gowanus Art Spine.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .timeline-container {
    margin: 4rem 0;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .tl-wrap {
    border-left: 4px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-dark) 20%, transparent);
    margin-left: 3rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tl-gap {
    margin-left: -5px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .gap-1 { height: 60px; }
  .gap-2 { height: 75px; }
  .gap-3 { height: 180px; }

  .tl-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tl-item.right {
    padding-left: 45%;
  }

  /* Nodes */
  .tl-node {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: -23px;
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tl-node.accent {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px #fff, 0 0 0 7px var(--color-accent);
  }

  .tl-node.dark {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px #fff, 0 0 0 7px var(--color-dark);
    margin-left: -23px;
  }

  /* Card */
  .tl-card {
    background: #fff;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 520px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .tl-card-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .tl-card-inner.reverse {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  /* Text side */
  .tl-text {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  /* Image side */
  .tl-image {
    width: 160px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tl-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: none;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Labels */
  .phase {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .phase.accent { background: var(--color-accent); }
  .phase.dark   { background: var(--color-dark); }

  .time-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .time-label.accent { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .time-label.dark   { color: var(--color-dark); }

  .tl-text h4 { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .tl-text p  { margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 100%; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tl-item.right { padding-left: 0; }

    .tl-image { width: 120px; }
  }
</style>